8 Drawbacks & Limits
********************

  1. There might be bugs on emacs-nu
  2. Emacs-nu is meant for azerty, qwzerty.  It would not be very good
     with other layouts However the plan for other layouts might be
     simple.  Control + key should stick to the mnemonic, like Ctrl+s
     to display save prompt.  While immediate keys like Alt+s or,
     obviously, the paddle Alt+i / Alt+j / Alt+k / Alt+l, should be
     transposed according to layout.  Control+h key to display Cheat
     Sheet, plus prompts, will help memorizing.


