9 Contributing
**************

Emacs nu is moving to a "one file per feature" style.  There are files
for common, core nu-mode, then files for integrating it.  For example
there is a nu-isearch.el file, a nu-ibuffer.el file.  I do expect to
isolate a file per mode.


